      <section eId="sec_473_B">
        <num>473-B</num>
        <heading>Reporting of endangered adults; persons in need of protective services</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_473_B__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>reports or refers such person to the department, office for the\naging, or any local social services district office or designated area\nagency on aging, law enforcement agency, or any other person, agency or\norganization that such person, in good faith, believes will take\nappropriate action; or\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_473_B__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>testifies in any judicial or administrative proceeding arising\nfrom such report or referral shall have immunity from any civil\nliability that might otherwise result by reason of the act of making\nsuch report or referral or of giving of such testimony.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
